			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "From tutorial\r\nDebug book → Go to Region → Act 2 → SCL → Entry Point Mountain Pass \r\nDebug book → Act 2 Setup → Absolute path: gives Spider's lyre to unlock the Drider's path.\r\nin reCon: teleport S_SCL_DriderCaravan_HalfOrcCaster \r\nSay you are true soul\r\ntalk to him again  → play lyre to draw in drider\r\ntalk to drider → choose to go to moonrise → follow drider to ambush point\r\nIn ambush dialogue → turn on drider and side with harpers\r\nIn combat → ctrl k all harpers first except S_SCL_Drider_Harper_Ranger_001 (Harper Skywin) and then drider\r\nTalk to Harper Skywin"
				},
